ah, @danny.lan, `isFieldMatch` fails now because for the field, `function_args: undefined`, but for the extracted field, there's no `function_args`, so the `isEqual(arg.fieldRefinements..., split.fieldRefinements...)` is false
do you know why we have `function_args: undefined` for the field we're doing a `useExtract` on? or uh, idk what the fix should be here
ah interesting… this must have been caused by my derived field PR (which now that i look at it, passed cypress flakily)
Another catch by Cypress!!!! This makes finding bugs much more exciting
